snippet.title: LAZERZ Release Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to LAZERZ! The fast paced, free to play arena shooter. Master the art of hydraulic power movement and wall running. Fly like an angel through the arena and shoot with powerful ricocheting lazerz to obliterate your enemies with style!

LAZERZ currently offers Free For All chaos and the precursor ranking for highly detailed statistics about your ingame performance.
Let's shoot some lazerz... with style!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2896440/LAZERZ/
